{"tid":12805,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"頭號大毒梟越獄逃亡 不忘做睪丸植入護雄風","createTime":"2016-11-29T21:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T22:24:01.000Z","uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5549dc4613dbe6ea8d4d7912e393f87e554e3eb9","tid":12805,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:28:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160116/640_c90e682cd3d865b978aa7deb1f71d844.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160116%2F640_c90e682cd3d865b978aa7deb1f71d844.jpg&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsH8C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=7dd6416e\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160116/640_c90e682cd3d865b978aa7deb1f71d844.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n墨西哥大毒梟古茲曼('El Chapo' Guzman)去年7月再度成功越獄，不過就在上周他還是被抓回了牢裡。但現在有消息指出，就在他逃亡期間，他曾經接受過睪丸植入手術，來治療勃起功能障礙，重振雄風。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，監獄醫療團隊為古茲曼進行的體檢報告在8日公布指出，去年9~10月古茲曼逃亡期間，曾到他集團控制下的一間診所，進行睪丸植入手術，來重振雄風，報告還稱「背部、臀部及生殖器官的疤痕就是證據」。<br />\n<br />\n調查人員也表示，在捉拿古茲曼後，從他身上搜出可注射睾丸酮、針筒、抗生素及價值逾250美元(約新台幣7500元)的治療性功能藥物。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"d159e13086e7c9b39481f006489398e8a14f9538","tid":12805,"uid":20524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T22:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能鑲金鑲鑽鑲珠係條jer到呢"},{"pid":"8c98037da726ce5aee00137a7201680ccce87f08","tid":12805,"uid":6829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T22:24:01.000Z","msg":"重振雄風之後入返去坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}